msgid "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)"
msgstr "检索增强生成 (RAG)"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:78
msgid "Combine LLM with your document knowledge base using Milvus vector search."
msgstr "使用 Milvus 向量搜索将 LLM 与您的文档知识库结合。"

