msgid "Inherit ``MilvusRAG`` capability for vector search"
msgstr "继承 ``MilvusRAG`` 能力以进行向量搜索"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:159
msgid "``init_client()`` initializes the Milvus connection"
msgstr "``init_client()`` 初始化 Milvus 连接"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:160
msgid "``view()`` creates or opens a collection"
msgstr "``view()`` 创建或打开集合"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:161
msgid "``consume_string()`` ingests documents"
msgstr "``consume_string()`` 导入文档"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:162
msgid "``aask_retrieved()`` combines retrieval with generation"
msgstr "``aask_retrieved()`` 将检索与生成结合"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:165
msgid "Code Review"
msgstr "代码审查"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:167
msgid "Automated code review with structured output."
msgstr "自动化代码审查，输出结构化结果。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:211
msgid "``Review`` capability provides structured review methods"
msgstr "``Review`` 能力提供结构化的审查方法"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:212
msgid "``review_string()`` returns a structured review result"
msgstr "``review_string()`` 返回结构化的审查结果"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:213
msgid "``supervisor_check()`` adds LLM validation layer"
msgstr "``supervisor_check()`` 添加 LLM 验证层"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:214
msgid "Results have ``display()`` for formatted output"
msgstr "结果具有 ``display()`` 方法用于格式化输出"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:217
msgid "Code Correction"
msgstr "代码修正"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:219
msgid "Review code and automatically apply corrections based on review feedback."
msgstr "审查代码并根据审查反馈自动应用修正。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:264
msgid ""
"Combine ``Review`` and ``Correct`` capabilities for review-correction "
"workflow"
msgstr "结合 ``Review`` 和 ``Correct`` 能力实现审查-修正工作流"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:265
msgid "``review_string()`` with topic parameter for focused reviews"
msgstr "``review_string()`` 使用 topic 参数进行有针对性的审查"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:266
msgid "``correct_string()`` applies improvements identified in review"
msgstr "``correct_string()`` 应用审查中发现的改进"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:269
msgid "Task Proposal"
msgstr "任务提案"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:271
msgid "Let the LLM propose tasks based on objectives."
msgstr "让 LLM 根据目标提议任务。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:313
msgid "``ProposeTask`` capability lets LLM decompose objectives into tasks"
msgstr "``ProposeTask`` 能力让 LLM 将目标分解为任务"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:314
msgid "``mode=\"agentic\"`` for complex autonomous decomposition"
msgstr "``mode=\"agentic\"`` 用于复杂的自主分解"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:315
msgid "``mode=\"standard\"`` for simpler task proposals"
msgstr "``mode=\"standard\"`` 用于较简单的任务提案"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:316
msgid "Iterate over proposed tasks and delegate each"
msgstr "遍历提出的任务并逐一分派"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:319
msgid "Structured Output"
msgstr "结构化输出"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:321
msgid "Get type-safe responses from LLM using Pydantic models."
msgstr "使用 Pydantic 模型从 LLM 获取类型安全的响应。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:366
msgid "Define Pydantic model with expected fields"
msgstr "定义包含预期字段的 Pydantic 模型"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:367
msgid "``aask_structured()`` returns typed instance"
msgstr "``aask_structured()`` 返回带类型的实例"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:368
msgid "Automatic validation of LLM response"
msgstr "自动验证 LLM 响应"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:371
msgid "Extracting Structured Data"
msgstr "提取结构化数据"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:373
msgid "Extract information from unstructured text."
msgstr "从非结构化文本中提取信息。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:421
msgid "``Extract`` capability for structured extraction from text"
msgstr "``Extract`` 能力用于从文本中进行结构化提取"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:422
msgid "``extract_string()`` parses text into Pydantic model"
msgstr "``extract_string()`` 将文本解析为 Pydantic 模型"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:423
msgid "Support for optional fields with defaults"
msgstr "支持带有默认值的可选字段"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:426
msgid "Diff Editing"
msgstr "差异编辑"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:428
msgid ""
"Automatically fix spelling, wording, and other text issues with diff-"
"based editing."
msgstr "通过基于差异的编辑自动修复拼写、措辞和其他文本问题。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:470
msgid "``DiffEdit`` capability for automatic text correction"
msgstr "``DiffEdit`` 能力用于自动文本修正"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:471
msgid "``diff_edit()`` applies fixes while preserving meaning"
msgstr "``diff_edit()`` 在保留原意的同时应用修复"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:472
msgid "``to_task_output()`` converts action result to task output"
msgstr "``to_task_output()`` 将动作结果转换为任务输出"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:473
msgid "``delegate_blocking()`` for synchronous execution"
msgstr "``delegate_blocking()`` 用于同步执行"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:476
msgid "Rule-Based Processing"
msgstr "基于规则的处理"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:478
msgid "Apply structured rules to content."
msgstr "对内容应用结构化规则。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:532
msgid "Define rules with ``RuleSet`` - each rule has pattern, action, and message"
msgstr "使用 ``RuleSet`` 定义规则——每条规则包含模式、动作和消息"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:533
msgid "Actions: ``reject`` blocks content, ``replace`` substitutes text"
msgstr "动作：``reject`` 阻止内容，``replace`` 替换文本"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:534
msgid "``apply_rules()`` processes content through all matching rules"
msgstr "``apply_rules()`` 通过所有匹配的规则处理内容"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:535
msgid "Rules are executed in order, first match determines action"
msgstr "规则按顺序执行，第一个匹配项决定动作"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:538
msgid "Content Improvement"
msgstr "内容优化"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:540
msgid "Improve writing quality with style and clarity enhancements."
msgstr "通过风格和清晰度增强来提升写作质量。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:582
msgid "``Improve`` capability for content enhancement"
msgstr "``Improve`` 能力用于内容增强"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:583
msgid "``improve_string()`` with style and focus parameters"
msgstr "``improve_string()`` 支持风格和焦点参数"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:584
msgid "Multiple improvement dimensions supported"
msgstr "支持多个改进维度"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:587
msgid "Task Handling with File Operations"
msgstr "带有文件操作的任务处理"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:589
msgid "Write and save generated content to files using tool execution."
msgstr "使用工具执行将生成的内容写入并保存到文件。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:673
msgid "``HandleTask`` capability enables tool execution within actions"
msgstr "``HandleTask`` 能力支持在动作中执行工具"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:674
msgid "``fs_toolbox`` provides file system operations (write, read, etc.)"
msgstr "``fs_toolbox`` 提供文件系统操作（写入、读取等）"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:675
msgid "``handle()`` executes skills with input/output schema"
msgstr "``handle()`` 使用输入/输出模式执行技能"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:676
msgid "Chain multiple actions in a WorkFlow for pipeline execution"
msgstr "在 WorkFlow 中链接多个动作以实现流水线执行"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:677
msgid "``dependencies_prompt`` passes data between workflow steps"
msgstr "``dependencies_prompt`` 在工作流步骤之间传递数据"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:680
msgid "Task Cancellation and Checkpoint"
msgstr "任务取消与检查点"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:682
msgid "Cancel long-running tasks and retrieve partial outputs."
msgstr "取消长时间运行的任务并获取部分输出。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:758
msgid "``publish()`` triggers a workflow without waiting"
msgstr "``publish()`` 触发工作流但不等待完成"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:759
msgid "``cancel()`` stops task execution"
msgstr "``cancel()`` 停止任务执行"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:760
msgid "``get_output()`` retrieves partial results after cancellation"
msgstr "``get_output()`` 在取消后获取部分结果"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:761
msgid "``extra_init_context`` provides initial state for workflows"
msgstr "``extra_init_context`` 为工作流提供初始状态"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:764
msgid "Diary Generation from Commit History"
msgstr "从提交历史生成日记"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:766
msgid "Generate diaries from structured data like git commits."
msgstr "从 git 提交等结构化数据生成日记。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:879
msgid "``read_dependency()`` reads external files with a registered reader"
msgstr "``read_dependency()`` 使用注册的读取器读取外部文件"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:880
msgid "``goals`` list guides LLM behavior for structured output"
msgstr "``goals`` 列表引导 LLM 行为以实现结构化输出"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:881
msgid "``override_dependencies()`` replaces dependency source"
msgstr "``override_dependencies()`` 替换依赖来源"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:882
msgid "``move_to()`` redirects task to a different event/workflow"
msgstr "``move_to()`` 将任务重定向到不同的事件/工作流"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:885
msgid "Article Extraction and Storage"
msgstr "文章提取与存储"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:887
msgid "Extract key essence from articles and store in vector database."
msgstr "从文章中提取核心要点并存储到向量数据库。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:974
msgid "``ExtractArticleEssence`` extracts key content from articles"
msgstr "``ExtractArticleEssence`` 从文章中提取关键内容"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:975
msgid "``FixArticleEssence`` post-processes extracted content"
msgstr "``FixArticleEssence`` 对提取的内容进行后处理"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:976
msgid "``PersistentAll`` saves extracted data to disk"
msgstr "``PersistentAll`` 将提取的数据保存到磁盘"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:977
msgid "``InjectToDB`` stores processed data in vector database"
msgstr "``InjectToDB`` 将处理后的数据存储到向量数据库"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:978
msgid "``gather_files`` collects files matching pattern"
msgstr "``gather_files`` 收集匹配模式的文件"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:979
msgid "Custom ``reader`` function for domain-specific file handling"
msgstr "自定义 ``reader`` 函数用于特定领域的文件处理"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:982
msgid "Anki Deck Generation"
msgstr "Anki 牌组生成"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:984
msgid "Generate Anki flashcards from CSV question banks."
msgstr "从 CSV 题库生成 Anki 闪卡。"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:1063
msgid "``GenerateDeck`` capability for flashcard generation"
msgstr "``GenerateDeck`` 能力用于闪卡生成"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:1064
msgid "``generate_deck()`` creates deck from CSV column names and requirements"
msgstr "``generate_deck()`` 根据 CSV 列名和需求创建牌组"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:1065
msgid "``add_csv_data()`` associates question bank data with deck"
msgstr "``add_csv_data()`` 将题库数据与牌组关联"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:1066
msgid "``compile_deck()`` produces .apkg package for Anki import"
msgstr "``compile_deck()`` 生成供 Anki 导入的 .apkg 包"

#: ../../source/use-cases.rst:1067
msgid "``AppendTopicAnalysis`` provides topic analysis on CSV data"
msgstr "``AppendTopicAnalysis`` 对 CSV 数据提供主题分析"

